text:
People close to me know how much I love food. Infront of me is my favourite plate of desserts, cakes and pastries.
But this lockdown has changed me a lot. I havnt eaten from out since 3 months now. I am cutting down on eating non veg little by little. I appreciate simple home food more than fancy food. I dnt overeat ( I used to eat a lot and mostly junk ). This is definitely bcoz of things happening around us and grave situations where people are fighting for food. I dnt knw how many of you will relate to this but I just went writing down when I saw this picture taken in 2018 in some 5 Star hotel in Bangalore and makes me think will I ever look at the food the same way?
.
.
